Add your steps (pseudo-code) for the dice game here.

Display welcome message and explanation of game
Declare character variable that stores player's input
Display start/exit message
Process player's input:
    If input is s, start game
    If input is x, exit game and display exit message
    Otherwise, display start/exit message again
Declare two int variables
Store two random numbers between 1 and 6 in variables
Declare variable to store sum 
Calculate sum of random values and initialize variable with value
    If sum equals 7 or 11, display winning message
    If sum equals 2, 3 or 12, display losing message 
    Otherwise, sum becomes player’s point
        Declare two int variables
        Store two new random numbers between 1 and 6 in variables
        Declare variable to store sum 
        Calculate sum of random values and initialize variable with value
            If sum equals player’s point value, display winning message 
            If sum equals 7, display losing message
            Otherwise, player rolls again until win/lose conditions met
